items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three different Thursdays in a 20 day period.

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 40 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 9!

Everyone loves fresh beer, but obviously not as much as you do. You went straight to the source. 

That's a beer at 40 different venues categorized as a Brewery, Cidery or Meadery. Visit 5 more different ones for Level 9!

beer.beer_description: A dry farmhouse ale - think pear, apple, cracked pepper & hint of spice.

items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 115 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 24!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 30 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 7!

You have a keen taste for this Belgian masterpiece. Did you know the Saison style beer was invented by Belgian farms, brewed in the Winter and served the Spring/Summer to all their workers? Well now you do! That’s 5 different Saisons, Grisettes or Farmhouse Ales! Try 5 more for Level 2.
